# All values here are OPTIONAL. The dashboard ships with public defaults
# (no API keys, no signup, no GitHub secrets needed). Override only if you
# want to point at a private node or a different upstream during local dev.
#
# Copy this to .env.local to override. .env.local is git-ignored.

# Public Ethereum mainnet RPC. drpc.org is browser-CORS-friendly and free.
# Other public options: https://eth.llamarpc.com, https://eth.merkle.io,
# https://rpc.ankr.com/eth, https://cloudflare-eth.com
# VITE_RPC_URL=https://eth.drpc.org

# Public AaveKit V4 GraphQL endpoint (no auth required)
# VITE_AAVE_GRAPHQL=https://api.v4.aave.com/graphql
